						Integration</strong></th>
					<td style="padding: 3px 10px; border-left: 1px solid #9E9F9F; font-size: 12px; font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-weight: normal;"
						valign="top">#p_interfacename_in</td>
				</tr>'
;
        IF
            p_log_level_in = 'GLOBALERROR' AND p_log_stage_in = 'SCHEDULER'
